&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Grow with a team that believes developing talent is important, and is building that as a core strength of the company from day one.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Be a leader in the organization, leading the way for future sales hires and mentoring junior team members as they join.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
